possible for tanks to do their job, and ultimately you losing.  Hand in the froglok essence to Dolgin Codslayer, naked dwarf along the shore from the right of the tunnel.  Faydeder will immediately spawn in the water and come out to the tanks.  He is lvl 55, so I recommend tanks use disciplines like Mightystrike, high dmg/stun type /discs.  His fear, which is resisted a lot, and if not, only lasts 3 secs at most I would think if you have a good grp of 55ish there to help.  All you need to know. ;)<br>
<br>
